		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Weapon (@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.qpOD3sz47K9lnNgt]{Quarterstaff}) - Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p><em>This staff is between 6 and 9 ft. in length, and is used by travelers and adventurers to defend themselves. It can be effectively wielded in combat with two hands.</em></p><p><em>A magic weapon like this one has a bonus to attack and damage rolls and deals magical bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage.</em></p><p>You have a +2 bonus to attack rolls and damage rolls made with this magic weapon. While holding this weapon, you have &amp;reference[Advantage] on &amp;reference[Acrobatics] checks.</p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong></p><p>Cause the staff to emit green Dim Light out to 10 feet (toggle on/off, or after you roll Initiative).</p><p>Alter its form into a 6-inch rod or a 10-foot pole, or revert to a Quarterstaff.</p><p><strong>Reaction </strong>- Quarterstaff Form Only</p><p>When you are hit by an attack while holding the weapon, you can take a Reaction to gain a +5 bonus to your &amp;reference[Armor Class] against the triggering attack, possibly causing it to miss. You can't use this property again until you finish a Short or Long Rest.</p><p><strong>Properties:</strong></p><p>&amp;reference[magic weapon], &amp;Reference[Reach] (10 ft.), &amp;Reference[Handed], &amp;Reference[thrown] (30/120)</p>",
